Class TracingTaskListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.jvm.java.tracing.TracingTaskListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BuckJavacTaskListener

    public class TracingTaskListener
extends Object
implements BuckJavacTaskListener
    A BuckJavacTaskListener that traces all events to a JavacPhaseTracer. The event stream coming from the compiler is a little dirty, so this class cleans it up minimally before tracing.
